# Finalize ICS Core Features & Watchlist Management

This plan focuses on completing the "missing links" in the ICS Border Control System, moving from mock-ups to functional modules for traveler querying, watchlist management, and account security.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> A new "Watchlist" navigation item will be added to the Admin Sidebar.
> Restricted: Only Administrators can add or remove entries from the Watchlist.

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] Data Query & Security

#### [MODIFY] [server.js](file:///c:/Users/Mohammed/.gemini/antigravity/ics-backend/server.js)
- Add `/api/search` endpoint: Queries `crossings`, `applications`, and `watchlist` by Passport Number or Name.
- Add `/api/settings/password` endpoint: Allows authenticated users to change their account password.
- Add `/api/watchlist/:id` (DELETE): Allows Administrators to remove entries from the watchlist.

